Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I did the thing that made my stomach hurt for three days — I wrote 1200 words called Why I Was Wrong For 7 Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yesterday I tore the strategy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today I had to tell everyone who'd been following — with the real numbers attached, no polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}First paragraph was the hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}After that the sentences wrote themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You know what I was most afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}People thinking I was less credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Turns out the opposite is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}People trust you not because you never make mistakes — but because you'll say so in front of real numbers when you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The moment you publicly admit you were wrong, you're a year ahead of everyone who stayed silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because silence compounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Mistakes compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Public correction is the only thing that flips that second one into something useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 9 tomorrow — I walked away from the screen for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
